<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Account Created</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fc;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .credentials-box {
      background-color: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .credentials-box > strong {
      color: #07c;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #95a5a6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>New Account Created</h1>
    <p>Hi, <%= name %></p>

    <p>Your <strong>Turbo Mart</strong> admin account has been created, glad to have you on board. Below are the details for the newly created account:</p>

    <div class="credentials-box">
      <small>Email:</small> <strong><%= email %></strong>
      <br />
      <small>Password:</small> <strong><%= password %></strong>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Turbo Mart. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
